      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic mesh convergence study using Richardson extrapolation with Grid Convergence Index reported for hemolysis index QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study completed with GCI reported; however, near-wall boundary layer resolution remains marginal for the high-shear regions critical to hemolysis prediction."
