      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation (hemolysis index, shear stress distribution) must be directly linked to the clinical decision endpoint for the VAD device.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index is directly relevant; however, platelet activation index — a secondary clinical QoI — is not included in the validation scope."
